nodes.text: Gwhirrye Nekor was a male humanoid individual living during the Galactic War. Following the Battle of Asylum he travelled to Odessen and joined the Alliance against the Eternal Empire of Zakuul. He was assigned to the Underworld Logistics branch of the Alliance under Hylo Visz.
Gwhirrye Nekor appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire expansion as a vendor inside Odessen base.
